Hey everyone! The past few months worked out perfectly for us - not least thanks to all of you and your great support and feedback. You guys rock!

We are really blown away by your support for DENT! Please keep going - we love it!

Prepare for this awesome version 1.1.0. For the first time, you not only can send data volume but also airtime top-ups to your family and friends. AND: Your DENT app is GDPR-ready, as well.

Please leave us a review or send us your ideas, questions or warm greetings: support@dentwireless.com

Hi there, it’s us again with an update for your DENT App. Excited? Here you go!

We made DENT 1.3.0 much better by fixing some issues and improving the overall performance. 

And to all our German DENT fans: Your app is available in German now – bitteschön! Chinese as well? Shure thing!

What else can we do to make your DENT App even better? Write us a review or an email to support@dentwireless.com

Hi DENT folks, hungry for a new feature? Here you go! With DENT Voice you can call family and friends globally – no matter where you are. Simply select a contact from your address book and add minutes to the plan DENT is suggesting. Then call your loved one directly from the app! What do think about DENT Voice? Tell us by writing a review or send your feedback and questions to support@dentwireless.com

With the new version, we enabled DENT Data Plans for all eSIM-capable devices like iPhone XS, iPhone XR, iPhone 11, iPhone 11 Pro, and more.

With one eSIM, you can add data plans for over 50 countries worldwide. Travel without changing SIM cards anymore and forget about roaming fees. Just download your digital SIM card directly to your phone – simple & easy with no strings attached.

If you need help installing the DENT eSIM, please contact our support team: support-dataplans@dentwireless.com

DENT App 4.0 is now here, with the new DENT Marketplace! Buying and selling DENT eSIM Data is now possible in the latest app version under the Marketplace tab. Trading eSIM data with the size, validity, and price you want can happen right in the palm of your hand. If you're enjoying DENT App 4.0 let us know by leaving a review or if you have any questions, please reach out to our support: https://dentwireless.zendesk.com/hc/en-us
